cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper focuses on deep learning-based video object tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of memory and attention mechanisms also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of LSTM networks suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE), and the evaluation of the method on video datasets suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM).
